hopobject.body: Thanks for calling when does risperdal consta go generic In the paparazzi-crazed world of Hollywood, some stars still manage to slip away and have their special day in private. Check out the celebs who've snuck off for a secret wedding ... Zoe Saldana got hitched! The Hollywood actress secretly wed her boyfriend, Italian artist Marco Perego, in June — Us Weekly reports. "It was super-small but very romantic and beautiful," a source told the magazine of the quiet ceremony, which was attended by "just a few" close friends and relatives. While the couple is rarely photographed together, they have reportedly known each other for "a long time." Perego got together with the "Avatar" actress shortly after her split Hollywood star, Bradley Cooper, whom she dated on-and-off for two years. Congrats, Zoe!
